---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import LeadForm from '../components/LeadForm.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="FAQ | Supplemental Insurance Pros" description="Insurance supplementing FAQ.">
<section class="hero"><div class="container"><p class="eyebrow">FAQ</p><h1>Insurance supplementing questions.</h1></div></section><section><div class="container grid"><div class="card"><h2>What is insurance supplementing?</h2><p>A supplement is a documented request for additional covered scope or cost items that may not have been included in the original estimate.</p></div><div class="card"><h2>Do you guarantee claim approval?</h2><p>No. The site must not guarantee approval, payment, or outcome.</p></div><div class="card"><h2>Do you work with contractors?</h2><p>Yes. Contractors are a primary audience for supplement documentation support.</p></div><div class="card"><h2>What states do you serve?</h2><p>Tennessee and bordering states, subject to licensing and compliance requirements.</p></div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
